{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/maple/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"a2361f0f-4e31-52ab-86bd-cfb700942046","html":"<p>Maple is an app to manage the sales hierarchy in Vodafone. It allows to add new employees, assign them roles and targets and move them under new teams.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cb98864452d269a516f4cb9110f31ae0/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"Home page\"\n        src=\"/static/cb98864452d269a516f4cb9110f31ae0/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cb98864452d269a516f4cb9110f31ae0/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/cb98864452d269a516f4cb9110f31ae0/dbdff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Home page</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>In this project, I owned the 100% of the front-end build until it was published. Later on, I worked in a couple of more journeys (joiners/leavers, change teams) and features with another co-worker.</p>\n<p>Maple was built using VueJS, Vuex (to manage the global state) and the Material-UI library for Vue. It also uses a library called <a href=\"https://github.com/dabeng/OrgChart\">OrgChart</a> to build the organigram in the homepage. I also added a chatbot with speech recognition powered by <a href=\"https://dialogflow.com/\">Dialogflow</a> (formerly known as Api.ai).</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3fd6f456c7109c9d32890422d36d23ec/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"Adding a new employee\"\n        src=\"/static/3fd6f456c7109c9d32890422d36d23ec/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3fd6f456c7109c9d32890422d36d23ec/d1f95/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/3fd6f456c7109c9d32890422d36d23ec/dbdff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Adding a new employee</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 996px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bcad90f2ffc498fd7a278893a1e03aed/250bb/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"Targets\"\n        src=\"/static/bcad90f2ffc498fd7a278893a1e03aed/250bb/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bcad90f2ffc498fd7a278893a1e03aed/d1f95/3.jpg 500w,\n/static/bcad90f2ffc498fd7a278893a1e03aed/250bb/3.jpg 996w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 996px) 100vw, 996px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Targets</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>","fields":{"prefix":"2017"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Maple","categories":"vodafone vue vuex webpack material-ui web design ux inverted","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/ddaf7bdf7e702cf95b90d6a339351689/f3583/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/maple/","source":"work"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}